220
00:17:16,835 --> 00:17:19,326
- Better luck next time.
- Better luck, Burt.

221
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,734
There you go.

222
00:17:26,078 --> 00:17:27,875
- Well, thanks, love.
- Careful, it's hot.

223
00:17:30,249 --> 00:17:33,241
